[2026-07-06T11:56:29.346Z] [INFO] [stderr] +
[2026-07-06T11:56:29.346Z] [INFO] [stderr] +### 9.1 Inconsistent Design Between Pages
[2026-07-06T11:56:29.346Z] [INFO] [stderr] +|-------|-----|
[2026-07-06T11:56:29.346Z] [INFO] [stderr] +| Page titles used random formats (emoji, no icon, different text sizes, missing descriptions) | Created `PageHeader` component with consistent `icon + title + description + actions` pattern |
[2026-07-06T11:56:29.346Z] [INFO] [stderr] +| Issue | Fix |
[2026-07-06T11:56:29.346Z] [INFO] [stderr] +| Section spacing differed (some used `gap-6`, some `gap-8`, some `space-y-4`) | Standardized section spacing via `PageSection` component |
[2026-07-06T11:56:29.346Z] [INFO] [stderr] +| Card styles differed — some used Tailwind `rounded-2xl`, some `rounded-lg`, some hard-coded `12px` | All cards now use `var(--radius-*)` tokens consistently |
[2026-07-06T11:56:29.347Z] [INFO] [stderr] +| Badge styles varied — some used Tailwind, some inline `span` with direct styles | Unified to `Badge` component with 7 variants |
[2026-07-06T11:56:29.346Z] [INFO] [stderr] +| Page widths varied arbitrarily between `max-w-7xl`, `max-w-5xl`, `max-w-3xl`, or no constraint | Created `PageContainer` component with `full`, `wide`, `standard`, `narrow`, `chat` widths |
[2026-07-06T11:56:29.347Z] [INFO] [stderr] +| Empty/loading/error states missing or inconsistent on many pages | Applied `EmptyState`, `LoadingSkeleton`, `ErrorState` components consistently |
[2026-07-06T11:56:29.347Z] [INFO] [stderr] +| Button variants inconsistent across pages | Unified to `Button` component with 7 variants, 4 sizes |
[2026-07-06T11:56:29.347Z] [INFO] [stderr] +### 9.2 Modern Style Improvements
[2026-07-06T11:56:29.347Z] [INFO] [stderr] +
[2026-07-06T11:56:29.347Z] [INFO] [stderr] +
[2026-07-06T11:56:29.347Z] [INFO] [stderr] +|--------|-------|
[2026-07-06T11:56:29.347Z] [INFO] [stderr] +| Old admin dashboard look with flat colors and harsh borders | Modern soft UI with rounded cards, subtle shadows, clean backgrounds |
[2026-07-06T11:56:29.347Z] [INFO] [stderr] +| Default browser button styling | Polished `Button` component with smooth hover/focus states |
[2026-07-06T11:56:29.347Z] [INFO] [stderr] +| Boring gray cards with no visual hierarchy | Cards with subtle left-border `tint` accent, proper spacing, elevation |
[2026-07-06T11:56:29.347Z] [INFO] [stderr] +| Before | After |
[2026-07-06T11:56:29.347Z] [INFO] [stderr] +| Page headers with emoji or missing icons | Every page gets `PageHeader` with semantic `Icon*` component |
[2026-07-06T11:56:29.347Z] [INFO] [stderr] +| Chat UI with transparent button, no personality | Polished chat with avatar, suggested prompts, typing indicator, proper bubbles |
[2026-07-06T11:56:29.347Z] [INFO] [stderr] +- **Soft rounded cards** — `var(--radius-lg)` on cards, `var(--radius-xl)` on modals, `var(--radius-2xl)` on hero elements
[2026-07-06T11:56:29.347Z] [INFO] [stderr] +### 9.3 Overall UI Modernization
[2026-07-06T11:56:29.347Z] [INFO] [stderr] +- **Clean neutral background** — `var(--color-background)` with `var(--color-surface)` for cards
[2026-07-06T11:56:29.347Z] [INFO] [stderr] +
[2026-07-06T11:56:29.347Z] [INFO] [stderr] +- **Strong visual hierarchy** — `PageHeader` with large bold title, smaller description, action buttons
[2026-07-06T11:56:29.347Z] [INFO] [stderr] +- **Subtle shadows** — `var(--shadow-md)` on cards, `var(--shadow-lg)` on modals/dropdowns, `var(--shadow-elevated)` on floating elements
[2026-07-06T11:56:29.347Z] [INFO] [stderr] +- **Beautiful page headers** — `icon + title + description + optional actions` pattern on every main page
[2026-07-06T11:56:29.347Z] [INFO] [stderr] +- **Modern icons** — All icons from lucide-react via semantic `Icon*` mapping (134 icons)
[2026-07-06T11:56:29.347Z] [INFO] [stderr] +- **Consistent badges** — `Badge` component with 7 semantic variants
[2026-07-06T11:56:29.347Z] [INFO] [stderr] +- **Clear section spacing** — `PageSection` with consistent `gap`, `padding`, `margin` tokens
[2026-07-06T11:56:29.347Z] [INFO] [stderr] +- **Smooth hover states** — CSS `transition: all var(--transition-fast)` on interactable elements
[2026-07-06T11:56:29.347Z] [INFO] [stderr] +- **Polished loading skeletons** — `LoadingSkeleton` with shimmer animation, 5 variants
[2026-07-06T11:56:29.347Z] [INFO] [stderr] +- **Mobile-friendly navigation** — `MobileBottomNavigation` on small screens, sidebar on desktop
[2026-07-06T11:56:29.347Z] [INFO] [stderr] +- **Floating AI Tutor chat button** — Proper visibility, positioning, contrast, responsive behavior
[2026-07-06T11:56:29.347Z] [INFO] [stderr] +
[2026-07-06T11:56:29.347Z] [INFO] [stderr] +### 9.4 CSS Bugs Fixed
[2026-07-06T11:56:29.347Z] [INFO] [stderr] +
[2026-07-06T11:56:29.347Z] [INFO] [stderr] +
[2026-07-06T11:56:29.347Z] [INFO] [stderr] +| Bug | File(s) | Fix |
